title: nbn rollout to benefit Tablelands communities (Tablelands Regional Council)
text: ( Source : Tablelands Regional Council ) Over 7, 300 additional Tablelands properties will be able to access the National Broadband Network following the release of the nbn three-year construction plan. Tablelands Regional Council Mayor Rosa
